## Pre-Flight Tasks

### Critical (must complete before Mar 11)
- [ ] VPS auto-restart — wrap FFmpeg in shell loop so it restarts automatically if Restream drops connection
- [ ] Rebuild HoldtLoop.mp4 with `-g 12 -keyint_min 12` keyframe flags — fixes YouTube "Poor" stream health
- [ ] Harden VPS — change root password, create non-root sudo user, SSH key auth, disable root login

### On Arrival
- [ ] Get Greek SIM for AT&T hotspot at Athens airport (Cosmote or Vodafone Greece)
- [ ] Confirm GL-MT6000 power supply brick says Input: 100-240V
- [ ] Test wired internet → router → laptop before first stream

